2008-10-07 23:52  jannis

	* dialogs/keyboard-settings/frap-shortcuts-provider.c,
	  dialogs/keyboard-settings/frap-shortcuts-provider.h,
	  dialogs/keyboard-settings/keyboard-dialog.glade,
	  dialogs/keyboard-settings/xfce-keyboard-settings.c,
	  xfce4-settings-helper/frap-shortcuts-provider.c,
	  xfce4-settings-helper/frap-shortcuts-provider.h:
	  Make sure to register each provider when created.
	  
	  Each provider now automatically adds itself to the /providers
	  property of the shortcuts channel when it is created and not
	  already added.

