2008-09-14 21:11  jannis

	* xfce4-settings-manager/xfce-settings-manager-dialog.c:
	  Detect whether a settings dialog supports X-XfcePluggable before
	  trying to embedd it into the main dialog. If it doesn't, just
	  spawn it and don't switch to the socket view. If it does, define
	  the --socket-id parameter and try to embed the dialog.

